content.p: The Open-Source Geospatial Research lab was established late 2011 following the MoU signed between International Cartographic Association (ICA) and OSGEO foundation. It was the first of its kind in Southeast Asia and is playing its active role in promoting the similar establishment in the region. Activities telephone: +6 (03) 8924 8000 fax: +6 (03) 8924 8018
